microprocessor_definition.name: Modular Engine FADEC
microprocessor_definition.description: Modular engine Full Authority Digital Engine Controller by Lupus the Canine.

node.label: Desired RPS/Throttle
node.description: Desired RPS, engine my fail to start if bellow 3. In direct throttle mode used as throttle value.

node.label: Pressure (optional)
node.description: Air intake manifold pressure, if not connected controller will use internal estimator.

node.label: Air throttle
node.description: Connect to air intake manifold throttle node.

node.label: Fuel throttle
node.description: Connect to fuel intake manifold throttle node.

node.label: Engine On/Of
node.description: Activate to start the engine, turn off to stop it or reset starter limiter.

node.label: Desired stoichiometric (optional)
node.description: Controller will try to maintain this stochiometric value.

node.label: Desired temperature
node.description: Desired temperature of the engine. Engine my not be able to maintain desired temperature. 0 to disable, negative to force enable

node.label: Power
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

node.label: Fuel
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

node.label: Max Power
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

node.label: Fuel consumption
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

node.label: Power/L
node.description: The input signal to be processed.
